Wooden A very simple amulet, made of wood.
Bronze This bronze amulet feels old to the touch.
Gold You can feel magic flowing through this ring.
Emerald The emerald in this amulet was found at the heart of the great mountains in the east.
Crystalline A masterpiece crafted by the dwarves from a block of crystallized wisdom. It is decorated with precious gemstones imbued with magic by powerful wizards.

